{"1":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.95","c":"وَالْفَجْرِ","d":"wal-fajri","e":"wal-fajri"}],"a":{"g":"By the dawn"}},"2":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.6","c":"وَلَيَالٍ","d":"walayālin","e":"walayālin"},{"b":"1.2","h":"2.69","c":"عَشْرٍ","d":"ʿashrin","e":"ʿashrin"}],"a":{"g":"And [by] ten nights"}},"3":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.1","c":"وَالشَّفْعِ","d":"wal-shafʿi","e":"wal-shafʿi"},{"b":"1.0","h":"1.79","c":"وَالْوَتْرِ","d":"wal-watri","e":"wal-watri"}],"a":{"g":"And [by] the even [number] and the odd"}},"4":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.14","c":"وَاللَّيْلِ","d":"wa-al-layli","e":"wa-al-layli"},{"b":"1.0","h":"1.93","c":"إِذَا","d":"idhā","e":"idhā"},{"b":"1.7","h":"3.15","c":"يَسْرِ","d":"yasri","e":"yasri"}],"a":{"g":"And [by] the night when it passes,"}},"5":{"w":[{"b":"0.1","h":"0.25","c":"هَلْ","d":"hal","e":"hal"},{"b":"0.4","h":"0.81","c":"فِي","d":"fī","e":"fī"},{"b":"0.9","h":"1.68","c":"ذَلِكَ","d":"dhālika","e":"dhālika"},{"b":"1.7","h":"3.14","c":"قَسَمٌ","d":"qasamun","e":"qasamun"},{"b":"2.6","h":"4.5","c":"لِذِي","d":"lidhī","e":"lidhī"},{"b":"3.2","h":"5.79","c":"حِجْرٍ","d":"ḥij'rin","e":"ḥij'rin"}],"a":{"g":"Is there [not] in [all] that an oath [sufficient] for one of perception?"}},"6":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.8","c":"أَلَمْ","d":"alam","e":"alam"},{"b":"0.54","h":"1.56","c":"تَرَ","d":"tara","e":"tara"},{"b":"0.97","h":"2.34","c":"كَيْفَ","d":"kayfa","e":"kayfa"},{"b":"1.6","h":"3.5","c":"فَعَلَ","d":"faʿala","e":"faʿala"},{"b":"2.3","h":"4.6","c":"رَبُّكَ","d":"rabbuka","e":"rabbuka"},{"b":"3.1","h":"6.25","c":"بِعَادٍ","d":"biʿādin","e":"biʿādin"}],"a":{"g":"Have you not considered how your Lord dealt with 'Aad -","ihya":"\n        <div class=\"ihya-tafsir-box\" style=\"margin-top: 15px; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 10px;\">\n            <h5 style=\"color: #91740c; font-family: Cabin, sans-serif;\">Tafsir Al-Ihya</h5>\n            <div class=\"ihya-arabic\" style=\"font-family: IndoPak; font-size: 18px; text-align: right; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #555;\">\n                فتارة يتعرف إليهم في أفعاله المخوفة والمرجوة فيتلو عليهم سنته في أعدائه وفي أنبيائه فيقول: \"ألم تر كيف فعل ربك بعاد إرم ذات العماد - ألم تر كيف فعل ربك بأصحاب الفيل\".\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"ihya-english\" style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; color: #777;\">\n                Indeed, at times He makes Himself known to them through His acts that inspire fear and hope, and He recites to them His established way [sunnah] with His enemies and with His prophets, saying: \"Have you not seen how your Lord dealt with 'Aad, Iram of the pillars [Iram dhat al-'imad]? Have you not seen how your Lord dealt with the companions of the elephant [ashab al-fil]?\"\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        "}},"7":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.15","c":"إِرَمَ","d":"irama","e":"irama"},{"b":"0.55","h":"1.07","c":"ذَاتِ","d":"dhāti","e":"dhāti"},{"b":"1.2","h":"2.39","c":"الْعِمَادِ","d":"l-ʿimādi","e":"l-ʿimādi"}],"a":{"g":"[With] Iram - who had lofty pillars,"}},"8":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.3","c":"الَّتِي","d":"allatī","e":"allatī"},{"b":"1.0","h":"2.24","c":"لَمْ","d":"lam","e":"lam"},{"b":"1.4","h":"2.84","c":"يُخْلَقْ","d":"yukh'laq","e":"yukh'laq"},{"b":"2.4","h":"4.35","c":"مِثْلُهَا","d":"mith'luhā","e":"mith'luhā"},{"b":"3.3","h":"6.38","c":"فِي","d":"fī","e":"fī"},{"b":"3.6","h":"6.82","c":"الْبِلَادِ","d":"l-bilādi","e":"l-bilādi"}],"a":{"g":"The likes of whom had never been created in the land?"}},"9":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.45","c":"وَثَمُودَ","d":"wathamūda","e":"wathamūda"},{"b":"1.0","h":"2.09","c":"الَّذِينَ","d":"alladhīna","e":"alladhīna"},{"b":"2.1","h":"3.92","c":"جَابُوا","d":"jābū","e":"jābū"},{"b":"2.8","h":"5.08","c":"الصَّخْرَ","d":"l-ṣakhra","e":"l-ṣakhra"},{"b":"3.6","h":"6.73","c":"بِالْوَادِ","d":"bil-wādi","e":"bil-wādi"}],"a":{"g":"And [with] Thamud, who carved out the rocks in the valley?"}},"10":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.03","c":"وَفِرْعَوْنَ","d":"wafir'ʿawna","e":"wafir'ʿawna"},{"b":"1.2","h":"2.14","c":"ذِي","d":"dhī","e":"dhī"},{"b":"1.4","h":"2.58","c":"الْأَوْتَادِ","d":"l-awtādi","e":"l-awtādi"}],"a":{"g":"And [with] Pharaoh, owner of the stakes? -"}},"11":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"1","c":"الَّذِينَ","d":"alladhīna","e":"alladhīna"},{"b":"1.1","h":"2.84","c":"طَغَوْا","d":"ṭaghaw","e":"ṭaghaw"},{"b":"1.7","h":"4.05","c":"فِي","d":"fī","e":"fī"},{"b":"2.3","h":"4.53","c":"الْبِلَادِ","d":"l-bilādi","e":"l-bilādi"}],"a":{"g":"[All of] whom oppressed within the lands"}},"12":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.05","c":"فَأَكْثَرُوا","d":"fa-aktharū","e":"fa-aktharū"},{"b":"1.2","h":"2.26","c":"فِيهَا","d":"fīhā","e":"fīhā"},{"b":"1.8","h":"3.54","c":"الْفَسَادَ","d":"l-fasāda","e":"l-fasāda"}],"a":{"g":"And increased therein the corruption."}},"13":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.03","c":"فَصَبَّ","d":"faṣabba","e":"faṣabba"},{"b":"0.83","h":"1.27","c":"عَلَيْهِمْ","d":"ʿalayhim","e":"ʿalayhim"},{"b":"1.8","h":"3.15","c":"رَبُّكَ","d":"rabbuka","e":"rabbuka"},{"b":"2.7","h":"4.75","c":"سَوْطَ","d":"sawṭa","e":"sawṭa"},{"b":"3.3","h":"5.96","c":"عَذَابٍ","d":"ʿadhābin","e":"ʿadhābin"}],"a":{"g":"So your Lord poured upon them a scourge of punishment."}},"14":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.03","c":"إِنَّ","d":"inna","e":"inna"},{"b":"1.2","h":"1.6","c":"رَبَّكَ","d":"rabbaka","e":"rabbaka"},{"b":"2.1","h":"3.24","c":"لَبِالْمِرْصَادِ","d":"labil-mir'ṣādi","e":"labil-mir'ṣādi"}],"a":{"g":"Indeed, your Lord is in observation."}},"15":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.9","c":"فَأَمَّا","d":"fa-ammā","e":"fa-ammā"},{"b":"1.5","h":"2.5","c":"الْإِنْسَانُ","d":"l-insānu","e":"l-insānu"},{"b":"3.5","h":"5.09","c":"إِذَا","d":"idhā","e":"idhā"},{"b":"4.2","h":"6.18","c":"مَا","d":"mā","e":"mā"},{"b":"4.3","h":"6.51","c":"ابْتَلَاهُ","d":"ib'talāhu","e":"ib'talāhu"},{"b":"5.5","h":"8.29","c":"رَبُّهُ","d":"rabbuhu","e":"rabbuhu"},{"b":"6.5","h":"10.13","c":"فَأَكْرَمَهُ","d":"fa-akramahu","e":"fa-akramahu"},{"b":"8.0","h":"12.89","c":"وَنَعَّمَهُ","d":"wanaʿʿamahu","e":"wanaʿʿamahu"},{"b":"9.5","h":"15.33","c":"فَيَقُولُ","d":"fayaqūlu","e":"fayaqūlu"},{"b":"10.6","h":"17.21","c":"رَبِّي","d":"rabbī","e":"rabbī"},{"b":"13.2","h":"19.49","c":"أَكْرَمَنِ","d":"akramani","e":"akramani"}],"a":{"g":"And as for man, when his Lord tries him and [thus] is generous to him and favors him, he says, \"My Lord has honored me.\"","ihya":"\n        <div class=\"ihya-tafsir-box\" style=\"margin-top: 15px; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 10px;\">\n            <h5 style=\"color: #91740c; font-family: Cabin, sans-serif;\">Tafsir Al-Ihya</h5>\n            <div class=\"ihya-arabic\" style=\"font-family: IndoPak; font-size: 18px; text-align: right; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #555;\">\n                والمغرور إذا أقبلت عليه الدنيا ظن أنها كرامة من الله، وإذا صرفت عنه ظن أنها هوان، كما أخبر الله تعالى عنه إذ قال \"فأما الإنسان إذا ما ابتلاه ربه فأكرمه ونعمه فيقول ربي أكرمن وأما إذا ما ابتلاه فقدر عليه رزقه فيقول ربي أهانن\" فأجاب الله عن ذلك \"كلا\" أي ليس كما قال إنما هو ابتلاء نعوذ بالله من شر البلاء ونسأل الله التثبيت، فبين أن ذلك غرور. قال الحسن كذبهما جميعاً بقوله \"كلا\" يقول ليس هذا بإكرامي ولا هذا بهواني، ولكن الكريم من أكرمته بطاعتي غنياً كان أو فقيراً، والمهان من أهنته بمعصيتي غنياً كان أو فقيراً.\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"ihya-english\" style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; color: #777;\">\n                Indeed, the deluded one [al-maghruur], when the world [al-dunya] turns towards him, thinks it is an honor [karaamah] from God, and when it is turned away from him, thinks it is a humiliation [ihaanah], just as God, the Exalted, informed about him when He said: \"As for man, when his Lord tests him, honoring him and bestowing favor upon him, he says, 'My Lord has honored me.' But when He tests him and restricts his provision, he says, 'My Lord has humiliated me.'\" So God answered concerning that: \"No [kallaa]\" — meaning, it is not as he said; it is only a trial [ibtilaa']. We seek refuge in God from the evil of the trial, and we ask God for steadfastness. Thus, He made clear that this is delusion [ghuruur]. Al-Hasan said: He declared them both false with His saying \"No [kallaa],\" meaning: This is not My honoring, nor is this My humiliation. Rather, the honored one [al-kareem] is he whom I have honored through his obedience to Me, whether he be rich or poor, and the humiliated one [al-muhaan] is he whom I have humiliated through his disobedience to Me, whether he be rich or poor.\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        "}},"16":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.9","c":"وَأَمَّا","d":"wa-ammā","e":"wa-ammā"},{"b":"1.5","h":"4.13","c":"إِذَا","d":"idhā","e":"idhā"},{"b":"3.7","h":"5.19","c":"مَا","d":"mā","e":"mā"},{"b":"3.8","h":"5.5","c":"ابْتَلَاهُ","d":"ib'talāhu","e":"ib'talāhu"},{"b":"4.9","h":"7.25","c":"فَقَدَرَ","d":"faqadara","e":"faqadara"},{"b":"5.8","h":"8.59","c":"عَلَيْهِ","d":"ʿalayhi","e":"ʿalayhi"},{"b":"6.7","h":"10.07","c":"رِزْقَهُ","d":"riz'qahu","e":"riz'qahu"},{"b":"7.7","h":"11.86","c":"فَيَقُولُ","d":"fayaqūlu","e":"fayaqūlu"},{"b":"8.8","h":"13.76","c":"رَبِّي","d":"rabbī","e":"rabbī"},{"b":"11.0","h":"16.44","c":"أَهَانَنِ","d":"ahānani","e":"ahānani"}],"a":{"g":"But when He tries him and restricts his provision, he says, \"My Lord has humiliated me.\""}},"17":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.15","c":"كَلَّا","d":"kallā","e":"kallā"},{"b":"1.2","h":"3.45","c":"بَلْ","d":"bal","e":"bal"},{"b":"1.7","h":"4.24","c":"لَا","d":"lā","e":"lā"},{"b":"2.0","h":"4.9","c":"تُكْرِمُونَ","d":"tuk'rimūna","e":"tuk'rimūna"},{"b":"3.3","h":"7.14","c":"الْيَتِيمَ","d":"l-yatīma","e":"l-yatīma"}],"a":{"g":"No! But you do not honor the orphan"}},"18":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.04","c":"وَلَا","d":"walā","e":"walā"},{"b":"0.6","h":"0.94","c":"تَحَاضُّونَ","d":"taḥāḍḍūna","e":"taḥāḍḍūna"},{"b":"4.2","h":"6.04","c":"عَلَى","d":"ʿalā","e":"ʿalā"},{"b":"4.9","h":"7.34","c":"طَعَامِ","d":"ṭaʿāmi","e":"ṭaʿāmi"},{"b":"5.8","h":"8.97","c":"الْمِسْكِينِ","d":"l-mis'kīni","e":"l-mis'kīni"}],"a":{"g":"And you do not encourage one another to feed the poor."}},"19":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.76","c":"وَتَأْكُلُونَ","d":"watakulūna","e":"watakulūna"},{"b":"1.4","h":"3.13","c":"التُّرَاثَ","d":"l-turātha","e":"l-turātha"},{"b":"2.4","h":"5","c":"أَكْلًا","d":"aklan","e":"aklan"},{"b":"2.8","h":"6.16","c":"لَمًّا","d":"lamman","e":"lamman"}],"a":{"g":"And you consume inheritance, devouring [it] altogether,"}},"20":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.05","c":"وَتُحِبُّونَ","d":"watuḥibbūna","e":"watuḥibbūna"},{"b":"1.4","h":"2.46","c":"الْمَالَ","d":"l-māla","e":"l-māla"},{"b":"2.2","h":"3.92","c":"حُبًّا","d":"ḥubban","e":"ḥubban"},{"b":"2.9","h":"6","c":"جَمًّا","d":"jamman","e":"jamman"}],"a":{"g":"And you love wealth with immense love."}},"21":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.85","c":"كَلَّا","d":"kallā","e":"kallā"},{"b":"1.4","h":"3.19","c":"إِذَا","d":"idhā","e":"idhā"},{"b":"1.9","h":"4.37","c":"دُكَّتِ","d":"dukkati","e":"dukkati"},{"b":"2.8","h":"5.87","c":"الْأَرْضُ","d":"l-arḍu","e":"l-arḍu"},{"b":"3.6","h":"7.36","c":"دَكًّا","d":"dakkan","e":"dakkan"},{"b":"5.3","h":"9.58","c":"دَكًّا","d":"dakkan","e":"dakkan"}],"a":{"g":"No! When the earth has been leveled - pounded and crushed -"}},"22":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.29","c":"وَجَاءَ","d":"wajāa","e":"wajāa"},{"b":"2.2","h":"2.47","c":"رَبُّكَ","d":"rabbuka","e":"rabbuka"},{"b":"3.1","h":"4.16","c":"وَالْمَلَكُ","d":"wal-malaku","e":"wal-malaku"},{"b":"4.2","h":"5.92","c":"صَفًّا","d":"ṣaffan","e":"ṣaffan"},{"b":"5.8","h":"7.27","c":"صَفًّا","d":"ṣaffan","e":"ṣaffan"}],"a":{"g":"And your Lord has come and the angels, rank upon rank,"}},"23":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.85","c":"وَجِاىءَ","d":"wajīa","e":"wajīa"},{"b":"2.3","h":"3.41","c":"يَوْمَئِذٍ","d":"yawma-idhin","e":"yawma-idhin"},{"b":"4.4","h":"6.03","c":"بِجَهَنَّمَ","d":"bijahannama","e":"bijahannama"},{"b":"7.3","h":"10.4","c":"يَوْمَئِذٍ","d":"yawma-idhin","e":"yawma-idhin"},{"b":"9.3","h":"12.96","c":"يَتَذَكَّرُ","d":"yatadhakkaru","e":"yatadhakkaru"},{"b":"10.5","h":"15.2","c":"الْإِنْسَانُ","d":"l-insānu","e":"l-insānu"},{"b":"12.6","h":"18.11","c":"وَأَنَّى","d":"wa-annā","e":"wa-annā"},{"b":"14.4","h":"20.47","c":"لَهُ","d":"lahu","e":"lahu"},{"b":"14.8","h":"21.53","c":"الذِّكْرَى","d":"l-dhik'rā","e":"l-dhik'rā"}],"a":{"g":"And brought [within view], that Day, is Hell - that Day, man will remember, but what good to him will be the remembrance?"}},"24":{"w":[{"b":"0.06","h":"0.07","c":"يَقُولُ","d":"yaqūlu","e":"yaqūlu"},{"b":"0.91","h":"2.1","c":"يَالَيْتَنِي","d":"yālaytanī","e":"yālaytanī"},{"b":"2.4","h":"4.23","c":"قَدَّمْتُ","d":"qaddamtu","e":"qaddamtu"},{"b":"3.4","h":"6.25","c":"لِحَيَاتِي","d":"liḥayātī","e":"liḥayātī"}],"a":{"g":"He will say, \"Oh, I wish I had sent ahead [some good] for my life.\""}},"25":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.9","c":"فَيَوْمَئِذٍ","d":"fayawma-idhin","e":"fayawma-idhin"},{"b":"1.3","h":"2.76","c":"لَا","d":"lā","e":"lā"},{"b":"1.8","h":"3.88","c":"يُعَذِّبُ","d":"yuʿadhibu","e":"yuʿadhibu"},{"b":"2.9","h":"5.61","c":"عَذَابَهُ","d":"ʿadhābahu","e":"ʿadhābahu"},{"b":"5.8","h":"9.07","c":"أَحَدٌ","d":"aḥadun","e":"aḥadun"}],"a":{"g":"So on that Day, none will punish [as severely] as His punishment,"}},"26":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.5","c":"وَلَا","d":"walā","e":"walā"},{"b":"0.6","h":"1.47","c":"يُوثِقُ","d":"yūthiqu","e":"yūthiqu"},{"b":"1.5","h":"3.09","c":"وَثَاقَهُ","d":"wathāqahu","e":"wathāqahu"},{"b":"4.1","h":"6.4","c":"أَحَدٌ","d":"aḥadun","e":"aḥadun"}],"a":{"g":"And none will bind [as severely] as His binding [of the evildoers]."}},"27":{"w":[{"b":"0.04","h":"0.55","c":"يَاأَيَّتُهَا","d":"yāayyatuhā","e":"yāayyatuhā"},{"b":"3.0","h":"4.21","c":"النَّفْسُ","d":"l-nafsu","e":"l-nafsu"},{"b":"4.7","h":"6.13","c":"الْمُطْمَئِنَّةُ","d":"l-muṭ'ma-inatu","e":"l-muṭ'ma-inatu"}],"a":{"g":"[To the righteous it will be said], \"O reassured soul,","ihya":"\n        <div class=\"ihya-tafsir-box\" style=\"margin-top: 15px; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 10px;\">\n            <h5 style=\"color: #91740c; font-family: Cabin, sans-serif;\">Tafsir Al-Ihya</h5>\n            <div class=\"ihya-arabic\" style=\"font-family: IndoPak; font-size: 18px; text-align: right; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #555;\">\n                وأما فعله فقد ذكر في قوله تعالى: ﴿ ياأيها النفس المطمئنة ارجعى إلى ربك راضية مرضية فادخلى في عبادى وادخلى جنتى ﴾ {} ولنرجع الآن إلى الغرض فإن المقصود ذكر نعم الله تعالى في الأكل فقد ذكرنا بعض نعم الله تعالى في آلات الأكل.\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"ihya-english\" style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; color: #777;\">\n                And as for His action, it has been mentioned in His saying, the Most High: \"O soul [nafs] at peace [mutma'innah], return to your Lord, well-pleased and well-pleasing. So enter among My servants, and enter My Paradise [jannah].\" (89:27-30)\n\nAnd let us now return to the purpose, for the intended aim is to mention the blessings [ni'am] of Allah, the Most High, in eating. We have already mentioned some of the blessings of Allah, the Most High, in the instruments of eating.\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        "}},"28":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.3","c":"ارْجِعِي","d":"ir'jiʿī","e":"ir'jiʿī"},{"b":"2.3","h":"2.79","c":"إِلَى","d":"ilā","e":"ilā"},{"b":"3.0","h":"3.83","c":"رَبِّكِ","d":"rabbiki","e":"rabbiki"},{"b":"3.8","h":"5.48","c":"رَاضِيَةً","d":"rāḍiyatan","e":"rāḍiyatan"},{"b":"5.8","h":"8.59","c":"مَرْضِيَّةً","d":"marḍiyyatan","e":"marḍiyyatan"}],"a":{"g":"Return to your Lord, well-pleased and pleasing [to Him],"}},"29":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.03","c":"فَادْخُلِي","d":"fa-ud'khulī","e":"fa-ud'khulī"},{"b":"0.98","h":"1.72","c":"فِي","d":"fī","e":"fī"},{"b":"1.4","h":"2.44","c":"عِبَادِي","d":"ʿibādī","e":"ʿibādī"}],"a":{"g":"And enter among My [righteous] servants"}},"30":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.03","c":"وَادْخُلِي","d":"wa-ud'khulī","e":"wa-ud'khulī"},{"b":"1.0","h":"1.99","c":"جَنَّتِي","d":"jannatī","e":"jannatī"}],"a":{"g":"And enter My Paradise.\""}}}